WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.466 --> 00:00:01.933
Grandpa His Majesty

2
00:00:01.933 --> 00:00:04.166
I'm relieved when you come back.

3
00:00:04.166 --> 00:00:05.100
Are you all right?

4
00:00:06.100 --> 00:00:08.566
Du Chen, you saved my granddaughter this time.

5
00:00:08.566 --> 00:00:10.400
My neighbor didn't respond.

6
00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:14.266
In this way, my granddaughter will be given to you.

7
00:00:14.266 --> 00:00:16.633
Grandpa, how can you do this?

8
00:00:17.133 --> 00:00:19.300
Du Chen almost died trying to save you

9
00:00:19.366 --> 00:00:21.766
Isn't he worth your life?

10
00:00:27.333 --> 00:00:29.900
Don't worry, I'll make him change his mind.

11
00:00:30.400 --> 00:00:31.766
Thank you so much, Mr. Lin

12
00:00:31.766 --> 00:00:32.666
Oops Du Chen

13
00:00:32.666 --> 00:00:34.366
I really didn't see you wrong.

14
00:00:34.366 --> 00:00:36.666
You are now the head of the Du Consortium

15
00:00:36.766 --> 00:00:37.733
Wait for the wedding day

16
00:00:37.733 --> 00:00:40.166
I will definitely hand over the Lin family to you

17
00:00:40.366 --> 00:00:41.900
Hmm, Lin Laozhen

18
00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:43.133
Not quite right.

19
00:00:43.133 --> 00:00:45.733
Hey, my Lin family has no children.

20
00:00:45.733 --> 00:00:48.200
In the future, you just need to be nice to Qingyao

21
00:00:48.266 --> 00:00:50.500
The old man is relieved

22
00:00:56.166 --> 00:00:56.600
Du Chen

23
00:00:56.600 --> 00:00:58.800
The head of the Lin family sent a message saying that Lin Xian was going missing

24
00:00:58.800 --> 00:01:00.733
I don't think he has any intention of marrying you at all

25
00:01:00.733 --> 00:01:02.000
Don't look for him

26
00:01:02.133 --> 00:01:03.333
How is my good brother now?

27
00:01:03.333 --> 00:01:05.066
Du Feiyun is suspected of kidnapping

28
00:01:05.066 --> 00:01:07.200
Has been arrested by Seebus

29
00:01:07.200 --> 00:01:09.166
Plus the evidence we collected earlier

30
00:01:09.166 --> 00:01:11.333
I'm afraid I'm going to watch him for 20 years

31
00:01:11.333 --> 00:01:14.233
As for the Qin family, it should never come out in this life

32
00:01:14.866 --> 00:01:17.966
My little mother also bought a plane ticket to fly abroad

33
00:01:18.100 --> 00:01:21.133
It seems that this wedding will not be attended yet.

34
00:01:21.133 --> 00:01:24.000
Are you sure Lin Qingyao will come back for you?

35
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:25.500
He will come back for me

36
00:01:26.533 --> 00:01:27.333
inspector

37
00:01:29.266 --> 00:01:30.466
I promised to marry you.

38
00:01:30.466 --> 00:01:32.400
Miss Lin, you figured it out

39
00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.700
For the sake of you being hurt to save me

40
00:01:34.700 --> 00:01:36.233
I reluctantly promise you

41
00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:37.266
But

42
00:01:38.266 --> 00:01:39.666
You have to promise me a condition.

43
00:01:39.666 --> 00:01:40.566
What kind of condition?

44
00:01:40.933 --> 00:01:42.400
Let's go out with me for a while

45
00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:44.600
Otherwise I wouldn't have agreed to marry you

46
00:01:45.066 --> 00:01:49.900
OK, let's start with the easiest kiss.

